asterline-work-loop

This package provides the work-loop feature in a Asterline plugin repository.

The plugin targets Asterline plugin manifests and plugin-bundled lifecycle hooks.
Its v4.17.1 behavior is ported at LazyCodex commit
3d7416bff3e6c80ebf5542b4dd12f5c76298d46d and canonical source commit
ed0241d1af225d38de55fdbcf0baa0abc9a1465a. Asterline-specific durable
checkpoint policy is retained; unsupported Auggie team messaging and thread
resume behavior is intentionally not claimed.
